e":"tab-collage","blocks":{"tab-collage-0":{"type":"image","settings":{"image_position":"center center","heading":"CRAFTED FOR THE SENSES","description":"<p>You can see it in the soft lambskin leather, picked and stitched with exacting attention to detail. You can feel it in the precision-cut aluminium frame that's robust yet beautiful. Even the carry case tells the story. Timeless design, made to last for generations.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_size":"medium","button_style_secondary":false,"enable_highlight":false,"highlight_style":"marker"}},"tab-collage-1":{"type":"image","settings":{"image_position":"center center","heading":"LESS EFFORT. MORE EMOTION.","description":"<p>Quick set up, intuitive user controls and Bluetooth 5.1 allow you to connect easily to the devices you already love. And if you want to make a few sounds of your own, four microphones keep your voice crystal clear on calls.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_size":"medium","button_style_secondary":false,"enable_highlight":false,"highlight_style":"marker"}},"tab-collage-2":{"type":"image","settings":{"image_position":"center center","heading":"ALMOST-<em>UNREAL<\/em> COMFORT","description":"<p>So comfortable, it's like you're not wearing them at all. Oval memory foam cushions, soft top grain lambskin and a superior fit invite you to play all day.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_size":"medium","button_style_secondary":false,"enable_highlight":true,"highlight_style":"marker"}},"tab-collage-3":{"type":"image","settings":{"image_position":"center center","heading":"STANDOUR ACCESSORIES TO FIT","description":"<p>Dynasty Headphone’s finishing touches are made to be touched, with matching aluminium details and woven fabric encasing the audio cable, charging cable and flight adapter.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_size":"medium","button_style_secondary":false,"enable_highlight":false,"highlight_style":"marker"}},"28d772cd-0ee2-447d-8186-c9837111d070":{"type":"image","settings":{"image_position":"center center","heading":"FIDILITY THAT FLEXES","description":"<p>For the rare moments you'll take them off, Dynasty Headphone can be folded and placed into the custom hardcase, which is lined with a super soft textile finish. No matter how much you move, they'll be safe and sound.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_size":"medium","button_style_secondary":false,"enable_highlight":false,"highlight_style":"marker"}},"4e7e819e-05a4-4e3c-82fd-aed257c54b3c":{"type":"image","settings":{"image_position":"center center","heading":"MUSIC AT YOUR <em>FINGERTIPS<\/em>","description":"<p>More bass, more warmth, more you. Personalise your listening experience with the app. The equalizer and noise cancellation adjusters give you complete control over how you listen, with just a tap.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_size":"medium","button_style_secondary":false,"enable_highlight":true,"highlight_style":"circle"}}},"block_order":["tab-collage-0","tab-collage-1","tab-collage-2","tab-collage-3","28d772cd-0ee2-447d-8186-c9837111d070","4e7e819e-05a4-4e3c-82fd-aed257c54b3c"],"settings":{"layout":"text_first","text_box_position":"top","text_alignment":"left","image_ratio":"650px","make_collapsible_rows":false,"full_width":false,"show_divider":false,"heading":"","heading_size":"h1","heading_alignment":"center","heading_tag":"h2","mobile_layout":"text_first","mobile_text_alignment":"left","mobile_image_ratio":"250px","colors_button_label":"#ffffff","colors_button_background":"#1a1b18","colors_text":"#ffffff","colors_border":"#d2d5d9","colors_background":"#272c31","gradient_background":"","colors_highlight":"#aa723e","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36,"enable_highlight":false,"highlight_style":"marker"}},"16448079723140b4d6":{"type":"collage","blocks":{"16448079726c05f8a0-0":{"type":"video","settings":{"enable_video_looping":false,"video_url":"","description":"Describe the video for customers usin