 of their completely wireless earplugs. They can join you almost everywhere you go - even underwater.<\/p>","author":"Nikolay Balushev","enable_highlight":false,"highlight_style":"marker"}},"1644818997c04c6254-4":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"icon":"5","text":"<p>They look exquisite, sound excellent, and offer seamless connectivity between Xbox and Bluetooth devices.<\/p>","author":"Angela McCafferty","enable_highlight":false,"highlight_style":"marker"}}},"block_order":["1644818997c04c6254-0","1644818997c04c6254-1","1644818997c04c6254-2","1644818997c04c6254-3","1644818997c04c6254-4"],"settings":{"autorotate":true,"autorotate_speed":5,"hide_images":false,"show_divider":false,"heading":"REVIEWS FROM <em>THE EXPERTS<\/em>","heading_size":"h1","heading_alignment":"center","heading_tag":"h2","colors_highlight":"#aa723e","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36,"enable_highlight":true,"highlight_style":"solid-color"}},"1644745953392511db":{"type":"newsletter","blocks":{"16447459539c38746f-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<em>SUBSCRIBE<\/em> TO OUR EMAILS","heading_tag":"h2","enable_highlight":true,"highlight_style":"bold-underline"}},"16447459539c38746f-1":{"type":"paragraph","settings":{"paragraph":"<p>Be the first to know about new collections and exclusive <em>offers<\/em>.<\/p>","enable_highlight":true,"highlight_style":"modern-underline"}},"16447459539c38746f-2":{"type":"email_form","settings":{}}},"block_order":["16447459539c38746f-0","16447459539c38746f-1","16447459539c38746f-2"],"settings":{"return_url":"","text_alignment":"left","mobile_text_alignment":"left","full_width":false,"show_divider":false,"colors_text":"#fafafa","colors_border":"#fafafa","colors_background":"#18181a","gradient_background":"","colors_highlight":"#ffb503","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"1644821694668dc64a":{"type":"map","blocks":{"1644821694a2720bf8-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Our Store","heading_size":"h2","heading_tag":"h2","enable_highlight":false,"h